properties.label: abs
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the absolute value of x.

properties.label: acos
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the arc cosine of x in radians.

properties.label: asin
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the arc sine of x in radians.

properties.label: atan
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the arc tangent of x in radians.

properties.label: atan2
properties.info:
Params: [y, x]
Returns the arc tangent of y/x in radians, considering the signs of both arguments to determine the correct quadrant.

properties.label: ceil
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the smallest integer greater than or equal to x.

properties.label: cos
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the cosine of x (where x is in radians).

properties.label: deg
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Converts x from radians to degrees.

properties.label: exp
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the value of e raised to the power of x (i.e., e^x).

properties.label: floor
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the largest integer less than or equal to x.

properties.label: fmod
properties.info:
Params: [x, y]
Returns the remainder of x divided by y.

properties.label: frexp
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns two values: the mantissa and the exponent of x such that x = mantissa * 2^exponent.

properties.label: huge
properties.info: Represents positive infinity.

properties.label: ldexp
properties.info:
Params: [m, e]
Returns m * 2^e. It is the inverse of math.frexp.

properties.label: log
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the natural logarithm (base e) of x.

properties.label: log10
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the base-10 logarithm of x.

properties.label: max
properties.info:
Params: [x, ...]
Returns the largest of its arguments.

properties.label: min
properties.info:
Params: [x, ...]
Returns the smallest of its arguments.

properties.label: modf
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the integer and fractional parts of x as a pair (integer, fractional).

properties.label: pi
properties.info: The constant pi, approximately 3.14159.

properties.label: pow
properties.info:
Params: [x, y]
Returns x raised to the power of y (x^y).

properties.label: rad
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Converts x from degrees to radians.

properties.label: random
properties.info:
Params: [m, n] (optional)
If two arguments are given, returns a random integer between m and n. If no arguments are provided, returns a floating-point number in the range [0, 1).

properties.label: randomseed
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Seeds the random number generator with the value x.

properties.label: sin
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the sine of x (where x is in radians).

properties.label: sinh
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the hyperbolic sine of x.

properties.label: sqrt
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the square root of x.

properties.label: tan
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the tangent of x (where x is in radians).

properties.label: tanh
properties.info:
Params: [x]
Returns the hyperbolic tangent of x.
